"title: WinRAR Extraction of Suspicious Files
id: 7d1d8da0-f5a6-4c1b-9a2c-1234567890ab
status: experimental
description: Detects the creation of specific suspicious files (DefragmentSrv, justice.exe, wayzgoose.dll) by the WinRAR process.
references:
    - Internal Lab Observation
author: Gemini
date: 2026/02/09
logsource:
    category: file_event
    product: windows
detection:
    selection_process:
        Image|endswith: '\WinRAR.exe'
    selection_files:
        TargetFilename|endswith: 
            - '\DefragmentSrv.exe'
            - '\DefragmentSrv.bat'
            - '\justice.exe'
            - '\wayzgoose.dll'
    condition: selection_process and selection_files
falsepositives:
    - Manual administrative recovery of specifically named backup files.
level: critical"
